6:
I think everyone had a blast at the
charity concert.
15:
Hey, everyone! Wanna tell me what
your dreams are?
18:
I wanna join the Guild Knights when I
grow up!
20: I want to be a veterinarian!
23:
That's awesome! I'll be cheering you
on every step of the way!
29:
I'm going to be an adventurer in the
Kaleidoscope!
33:
What! I said I'm never giving up,
didn't I?!
36:
Hey, come on! There's nothing
wrong with having a big dream!
45:
The doctor said his body is naturally
frail, and exercising too much isn't
safe for him...
47:
I'm going to train my body, cure my
disease... and become an
adventurer. I made a promise to my
dad before he died!
49:
As long as I work hard enough, my
dream will come true! Right,
Laputina?
58: What are you looking for at this hour?
62:
Oh, you two! Glad you stopped by.
Wanna help me pick out a book?
One that's filled with exciting
adventure!
67: Are you going to give it to Mark?
71:
Ahaha, that was quick. I'll never be a
real idol if you can read my face so
easily.
74:
You know, my body was weak when
I was little, too.
77:
I was afraid to have the prosthetics
installed, but I knew I wanted to be
an idol! So that's why—
80:
...I was able to overcome my
challenges, but I couldn't bring
myself to encourage that kid...
85: ...Is it okay if I ask why?
89:
I had a mom and dad. The chance
to have surgery was there for me.
91:
...But Mark? I wasn't sure what to say
to him.
94:
I got scared. I wasn't sure if it would
be okay to encourage him then and
there...
98:
...But still! It feels wrong to just stand
around and do nothing!
101:
My dream gave me strength, so I
wonder if maybe a book could help
him feel the same way? I might be
going about this the wrong way,
but...
105: ...All right. Let us help you out.
111:
Let's look for an exciting book
together.
120:
How about this one? It's called 'The
Wise Adventurer.' Looks like it's about
alchemy in the Endless Blue.
129:
Laputina! Mark's in trouble. He went
to the Kaleidoscope—
132: Crap, crap! What do I do here—
135: Idiot! If you die here, you'll never—
138: Shut up! Just let me do what I want!
140:
I'm going to be an adventurer, no
matter what! 
...It d-doesn't even matter why!
143:
B-because, I... If I don't, there's
nothing left for me—
152:
Even if your dreams never come
true... No, even if they DO! Either way,
that's not the end!
155:
As long as you never stop dreaming
for a better tomorrow, nothing's over!
158: But... This is all I have...
161:
Taking a different path is... scary, I
know. It takes courage.
164:
But, you know? You'll be just fine,
Mark. You'll find a new path, and it's
gonna be awesome.
173:
It doesn't matter if it takes a long
time, or you take a few detours
along the way. So...
177:
Let's look for a new dream together.
I'll always be in your corner, Mark!
184: Mark! Are you feeling all right?
188:
I've been thinking about my future a
lot... But I don't have an answer yet.
194:
But that book you lent me... It was
fun to read. That alchemy stuff is
pretty cool... I wanna read the next
one.
197: Okay! I'll bring it here for you!
201: All right, I've made up my mind!
204:
I'll become a super idol hero who
helps everyone achieve their
dreams... and I'll also help give them
the courage to take that first step!
208: Okay. You can do it, Lap-T.
213:
Your goals are getting bigger by the
day.
217:
Of course! The dreams of this super
idol hero are GALACTIC in scale!
